---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | TendersMW"
  description="TendersMW terms of service — rules and guidelines for using our procurement intelligence platform."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="glass-card p-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-muted">
      <p><strong class="text-text">Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text pt-2">Acceptance</h2>
      <p>By using TendersMW, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text pt-2">Service Description</h2>
      <p>TendersMW is a tender aggregation service that collects and displays publicly available procurement notices from government agencies, development organizations, and other public entities in Malawi.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text pt-2">Accuracy</h2>
      <p>While we strive for accuracy, tender information may contain errors or be outdated. Always verify details directly with the issuing authority before submitting a bid. TendersMW is not responsible for decisions made based on information presented on this site.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text pt-2">No Endorsement</h2>
      <p>Listing a tender on TendersMW does not constitute an endorsement of the procuring entity or the procurement process. We are an aggregator, not a procurement authority.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text pt-2">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>Tender data is sourced from public records. Our site design, code, and original content are the property of TendersMW.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text pt-2">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>TendersMW is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any losses arising from the use of our service.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
